flowchart LR
    BUDATA[BU Subscriptions - Source Data]
    INGEST[Ingestion and Chunking - Dev]
    BUDATA --> INGEST

    DEVF[Foundry Dev - EastUS2]
    DEVF --> DEVGOV[Shared Dev Governance]
    DEVF --> DEVSH[Shared Dev Services]

    DEVF --> BU1[BU Proj - Dev - BU1]
    DEVF --> BU2[BU Proj - Dev - BU2]
    DEVF --> BUN[BU Proj - Dev - BU N]

    BU1 --> BU1M[Models]
    BU1 --> BU1A[Agents]
    BU1 --> BU1V[Vector Index - In Project]
    BU1A -. query .-> BU1V
    INGEST --> BU1V

    BU2 --> BU2M[Models]
    BU2 --> BU2A[Agents]
    BU2 --> BU2V[Vector Index - In Project]
    BU2A -. query .-> BU2V
    INGEST --> BU2V

    BUN --> BUNM[Models]
    BUN --> BUNA[Agents]
    BUN --> BUNV[Vector Index - In Project]
    BUNA -. query .-> BUNV
    INGEST --> BUNV
